NEXT JS

-> Next js is fast than react

SEO(Search Engine Optimization) 

Setting up next js
  
-> npx create-next-app@latest

Folder Structure->
  -> jo bhi backened ka code hoga vo pages/api folder m jaayega

  -> agar hamlog koi bhi file pages ke andar banyenge to vo route ban jaaega aur us file ke andar jo bhi component ko hamlog export karoge to vo _app.js ke component ke andar aa jayega

Nested Routes
  ->if there is any file named index.js then it route will be "/";
  ->lets say there is a page called about.js then there is a route name "/about";
  -> lets say mene pages ke andar ek folder banya called user and mene uske andar ek page satwik.js banaya then it will be "/usr/satwik";
  -> lets say agar hum user pe jaaye aur vha pe mujhe kuch render karna h

